  "description": "A robust, production-ready CLI for log monitoring with API/Kafka output, SMTP email alerts, disk-based queue with optional compression, dead-letter queue, metrics, and full config via file or environment variables. Recent improvements: SMTP alerting, disk queue compression, decompression before send, dead-letter queue, enhanced metrics, and reliability fixes.",
  "main": "simple-cli.js",
